metadata.name: unconsciousness NO1
metadata.description:
In these series of draeings,   which were formed by using a kind of holy doodling method , I applied some sort of Improvised lines . Them completed them by adding purposely more detaied lines.
These portraits were created while I managed to connect with my inner state to form a doodle artwork. 
I tried to experience a state , similar to meditation,  and tend the people who confront my artworks to consider themselves,  staying away daily tensional life .
I used the symbols like DNA and heart and vibration and lines, because I think ,they can show a better situation of our mind. 
And I like ,when you look at these artworks,  you also have a journey into your subconscious.
